ideo": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBlxPIdk.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/hunleyeric/status/2073436880780382446", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "\ud80c\ude9d  before cable news, there were Saturday morning cartoons. \"No More Kings\" \u2014 Schoolhouse Rock's very first America Rock episode \u2014 taught a generation how we fired a king and built a free country. some lessons never get old. \ud83c\udf86", "last_comment_created": 1783242554429, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 51, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 42, "created": 1783180849000, "id": "2073436880780382446", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2073436710067924992/img/fZBn6qybuD_6wvCg.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2073436710067924992/pl/5AbgEMjmktjlmMEa.m3u8?tag=14", "aspectRatio": [4, 3], "heightRatio": 75, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2073436710067924992/vid/avc1/360x270/js2txi5gN0Cjs4vJ.mp4?tag=14"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1341019271594389504/fuJFq9z__normal.jpg", "displayName": "Eric Hunley", "username": "hunleyeric"}, "content": "\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8 Happy Independence Day!\n\nBefore cable news, there were Saturday morning cartoons. \"No More Kings\" \u2014 Schoolhouse Rock's very first America Rock episode \u2014 taught a generation how we fired a king and built a free country.\nSome lessons never get old. \ud83c\udf86\n#IndependenceDay #4thOfJuly", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 2902}}, "post_flair_text": "\u00a0\u00a0AMERICA\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0FIRST\u00a0", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlwIpzk", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 86, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "truth", "id": 8713880, "raw_content": "", "author": "ohpleaseuhhelpame", "created": 1783213817310, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "truthsocial.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBlwIpzk.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/posts/116864681605523102", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": " I will be there no matter what, but the \u201cwhat\u201d usually turns out to be a good thing. It\u2019s Saturday night, LETS HAVE SOME FUN, even if we are out late tonight. They say 11:00 O\u2019Clock for the speech. Who cares??? ", "last_comment_created": 1783213817310, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 86, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "Storms bring luck to whatever the occasion. They also make events a little bit more exciting! We will wait it out, I don\u2019t care if it\u2019s 2:00 O\u2019Clock in the morning, or in one hour from now. Looks like it is going to pass, they always do. I will be there no matter what, but the \u201cwhat\u201d usually turns out to be a good thing. It\u2019s Saturday night, LETS HAVE SOME FUN, even if we are out late tonight. They say 11:00 O\u2019Clock for the speech. Who cares??? Remember two weeks ago when the big UFC Event was at 100% chance of heavy rain, all week long, and just minutes before the card started. Well, there wasn\u2019t a single drop, and the fights turned out to be among the greatest in history, an event for the ages. Our great veterans, especially the old timers, many of whom are there, went through hellfire, and it didn\u2019t stop them. It\u2019s not going to stop us either! I\u2019m not going to let some rain stop our 250th. I\u2019m leaving the White House soon. God Bless America! President DONALD J. TRUMP", "large_image": "B7eElZdouw8oZj71.png", "title": "Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump)"}, "post_flair_text": "\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0TRUMP\u00a0\u00a0TRUTH\u00a0\u00a0", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2073552314363724137", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlwJ6Vm", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 82, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8713902, "raw_content": "", "author": "I-am-Orlando", "created": 1783214520170, "profile_picture": "TEnkk5XkT6JN", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "I_Love_45-70_Gov", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBlwJ6Vm.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/ImMeme0/status/2073552314363724137?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Lillington Guns & Ammo  4th of July  drone show of the Colt 1911 \r\n\r\n is going to trigger liberals ", "last_comment_created": 1783215220245, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 2, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 82, "is_edited": fa